                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-267-off1439 t18240916-267-crimeloc1441"></join>, two coach lamps, value 7 s.; two saddles, value 30 s.; three collars, value 30 s.; a pair of stirrup-irons, value 1 s.; a pair of pole-pieces, value 2 s.; a pair of collar braces, value 2 s.; a martingale, value 10 s.; a pair of pole braces, value 1 s.; a chaise pad, value 15 s.; a pair of traces value 10 s.; a pair of reins, value 5 s.; five bridles, value 3 l.; and a gig harness, value 50 s.; the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240916-267-victim2288" type="victimName">
